dcterms:description: This dataset keeps a record of the closing prices of the S&P 500 stocks from Jan. 1, 2003 to Jan. 1, 2008. It consists of 1258 samples for 452 stocks. The data have been preprocessed by taking logarithm and differencing transformations.
dcterms:title: S&P 500 stock data

dcterms:description: The NASDAQ-100 consists of 100 of the largest non-financial companies listed on the NASDAQ stock market. The dataset includes the closing prices of the stocks for each trading day from Jan. 1, 2011 to Dec. 31, 2011, which gives 252 samples in total. Differencing is applied to remove trends.
dcterms:title: NASDAQ-100 stock data

dcterms:description: Synthetic data generated based on the model described in the paper for experiments.
